%% Scania — Add dynamic service to cart → invoice checkout (POC). Flagship flow (SD-001, ADR-003, ADR-004).
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as Fleet Customer
    participant Yves as Yves (PDP / Cart / Checkout)
    participant Cart as Zed Cart<br/>(ScaniaDynamicService expander)
    participant SecmC as SECM Client
    participant SECM as SECM
    participant Checkout as Zed Checkout
    participant Sales as Zed Sales / OMS
    participant DB as Database

    Note over User,DB: Dynamic service line item — price locked at add-to-cart (ADR-004 gate: modelling still Proposed)
    User->>Yves: Add service (for vehicle) to cart
    Yves->>Cart: addItem(serviceRef, vehicleRef)
    Cart->>SecmC: getPrice(serviceRef, vehicleRef)
    SecmC->>SECM: GET /services?vehicle=… (price re-read)
    SECM-->>SecmC: Unit price
    SecmC-->>Cart: Price
    Cart->>Cart: Build dynamic item (service, vehicle, locked SECM price)
    Cart->>DB: Persist quote (cart survives sessions)
    Cart-->>Yves: Updated cart (services + optional regular products, multi-asset)

    User->>Yves: Proceed to checkout
    Yves->>Checkout: Summary (invoice only — no PSP, ADR-003)
    User->>Yves: Place Order
    Yves->>Checkout: placeOrder()
    Checkout->>Sales: Create sales order (invoice payment method)
    Sales->>DB: Persist order
    Sales-->>Yves: Order confirmation
    Yves-->>User: Order placed + OOTB confirmation email
    Note right of Sales: OMS then fires post-order FMAT notifications<br/>asynchronously (see oms-post-order-fmat)
